DEPENDENCIES
------------

+ eBox components
	
	+ ebox

+ Debian packages (apt-get install <package>)

	+ slapd
	+ libnet-ldap-perl

INSTALLATION
------------

- Once eBox base has been installed:
	
	./configure
	make install

  configure will autodetect eBox base path to install

- See debian/ebox-usersandgroups.postinst from ebox-usersandgroups deb
  package for details about LDAP configuration